Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.39,0:00:07.52,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Kurome...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:12.67,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, I joined the military \Nbecause I admired them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:15.30,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,I owe my life to a naval officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:17.53,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,I idolized him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.51,0:00:20.22,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,With weapon in hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.98,0:00:24.02,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,a soldier's duty is to protect \Nthe kingdom and its people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.11,0:00:27.18,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to become a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.28,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,But what, exactly, am I protecting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:42.52,SignA,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kurome's Snacks
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.18,0:00:48.29,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,So only four of us are left...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.88,0:00:50.55,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.89,0:00:52.19,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,This place has gotten a lot bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.42,0:00:53.62,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.14,0:00:56.00,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do, Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.00,0:00:59.20,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,After this is over, we'll be on the streets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:04.77,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who forced \Nme here in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.95,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,And before I knew it, it'd become this huge ordeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:10.04,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Was that how it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.81,0:01:15.07,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Then maybe I should take responsibility for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.76,0:01:17.54,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,G-Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.54,0:01:20.83,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, assassins being \Nuseless is a good thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.83,0:01:22.27,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,That's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.85,0:01:25.35,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,How about we join a traveling circus together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:26.10,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.10,0:01:27.52,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.10,0:01:30.15,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.44,0:01:33.65,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't say it like it's the last goodbye, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.08,0:01:35.99,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we reunite in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.38,0:01:37.66,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,is up to all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.90,0:01:39.51,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Well said.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:42.52,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,It'll take a whole lot to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.52,0:01:43.23,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.56,0:01:44.33,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:46.29,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.75,0:01:48.58,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.97,0:01:50.83,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,This is Night Raid's final mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.36,0:01:53.31,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Destroy the root of the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.31,0:01:55.29,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Take down Minister Onest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.41,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.81,0:02:04.26,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.81,Title1a,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(423,1)}Kill the Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.81,0:03:39.40,Title1b,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,598)}Kill the Emperor
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:43.03,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.88,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,the time you have depends on how \Nlong we can keep them occupied.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:48.51,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,You have to kill the minister within that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.26,0:03:50.60,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:55.02,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we revolt and start a new kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.96,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,We will overthrow the corrupt \Ngovernment with our own hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.51,0:04:01.34,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,and create a kingdom where \Ncitizens can live peacefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:03.30,Default,Everyone,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.67,0:04:07.74,Default - italics,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.59,0:04:12.74,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.74,0:04:14.69,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,This area is poorly constructed, just like we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.11,0:04:17.33,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly how Lubba mapped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.33,0:04:18.69,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:26.70,Default,Guards,0000,0000,0000,,Night Raid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:29.63,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wish to kill any more than necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:31.79,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who aren't ready to die, leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:33.37,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,That isn't an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:36.75,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,As expected, the guards protecting \Nthe interior are more determined.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.25,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice but to kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:44.17,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be able to handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.69,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:49.40,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Jaegers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.81,0:04:50.56,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:52.98,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.06,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,You remember me, Tatsumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.36,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you'd let us through,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.06,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.24,0:05:01.38,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:04.28,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Finishing a job I've started is in my nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.84,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.29,0:05:11.12,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Future historians will retrospectively \Ndetermine what is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.42,0:05:14.29,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need for you to lose your lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:15.29,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:15.95,Default,Guard,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:17.17,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.93,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,In fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.52,0:05:20.84,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.01,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.72,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,So that's his Imperial Arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:31.89,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,What you say is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.50,0:05:36.16,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,The capital is completely degenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.85,0:05:38.90,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,The current regime will surely collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.17,0:05:41.40,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that, why do you stand in our way?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.65,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Your methods involve too much bloodshed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:46.28,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say, you stubborn bastard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.53,0:05:48.57,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was formerly a teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.16,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:51.37,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone like that join the Jaegers?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:57.08,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Back in my hometown, bandits abducted \Nmy students, killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:01.43,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,However, the capital didn't deem it a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:04.10,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,After all, it was a very poor village.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:06.01,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,They were abandoned
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:07.80,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,by their capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:09.64,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I never knew you had such a past.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:13.89,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, which is why I bear a \Ngrudge against the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:16.72,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.64,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,you should be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.64,0:06:20.70,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,on our side!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:23.68,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to do it my own way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:26.30,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,to change the capital from within.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:30.53,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,But you went and started a violent rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.28,0:06:32.80,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,How annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:34.91,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let my fists do the talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.37,0:06:40.88,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Akame! Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.88,0:06:42.21,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.41,0:06:43.13,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.71,0:06:46.13,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,We can't all be held up here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.13,0:06:47.66,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:49.93,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sis, don't you dare die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:56.27,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, before you kill the minister, \Nlet me get a punch in, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.69,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,That said, I'll finish you off now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing personal, but your fate \Nwas decided once you chose that side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.53,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Say your prayers, teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:13.62,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.03,0:07:16.46,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,Trump card... God's Wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:20.28,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,It seems you grossly underestimated \Nmy close-quarters combat skill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.16,0:07:22.37,Default - italics,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:25.06,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Minister, how's the war progressing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.76,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't favorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.10,0:07:34.51,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Against the pompous rebel army, \Nour soldiers are withering.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.27,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,A rebellion...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:38.14,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Have I governed them poorly?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.14,0:07:39.15,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.15,0:07:41.25,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Even after your parents passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:44.77,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,you've upheld your position as emperor splendidly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.25,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,And I've been with you this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.78,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Assuredly, you've made no mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.32,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:54.41,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,You've always been by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:59.54,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency, the citizens are \Nbeing swayed by nonsense,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:02.85,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,a nonsense they call rebellion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:06.63,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,You must make an example of these traitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:08.49,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Blood will be spilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:12.46,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,But as emperor, you must be fierce!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:14.50,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,This pointless rebellion will settle down
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:16.85,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,once you demonstrate your authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.35,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:30.07,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.56,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,A rebel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:34.70,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Night Raid...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.89,0:08:37.29,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,What were the palace guards doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.64,0:08:43.71,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,There don't seem to be any other bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.27,0:08:47.73,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,The target is Minister Onest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:48.88,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Eliminate!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.67,0:09:00.31,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,The supreme Imperial Arms is already in motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:01.22,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Take that—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.22,0:09:02.68,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, ahem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:08.48,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,What you've begun has thrown \Nthe kingdom into chaos!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:10.16,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, listen to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:13.11,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,For a long time, the capital \Nhas been under tyranny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:16.60,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,And this whole time, the weak have suffered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.15,0:09:18.95,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much they hoped or prayed,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:21.11,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,no one ever came to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.12,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Even Sayo and Ieyasu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.62,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,They... They all died!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.77,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,A kingdom like that needs to change, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.33,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:34.53,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,you mustn't be deceived by these words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.10,0:09:36.56,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Minister Onest,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:39.43,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,you're the one who's been manipulating him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:40.92,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.92,0:09:44.72,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,I don't appreciate these false accusations \Nin front of the emperor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:48.06,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,I say this out of love... Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:49.32,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Quit babbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:51.53,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you hear what they're saying outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:53.61,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This empire is finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.12,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,You brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.13,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,shut your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.42,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Your Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.42,0:10:01.58,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Bring down the iron hammer \Non these foolish rebels!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.99,0:10:04.41,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,I am the emperor of this realm!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:08.04,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:15.17,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,The empire's trump card, Shikoutazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:19.30,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Its strength is comparable to that of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.32,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is God...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.46,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Those who've betrayed the empire
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.31,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,will be judged by God!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.31,0:10:30.94,Default,People,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.82,0:10:47.87,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:50.29,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,That is the legendary Imperial Arms—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:55.25,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,Shikoutazer? It truly exists?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:56.55,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,That minister...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:11:01.47,Default,Najenda,0000,0000,0000,,So this is why he hasn't admitted defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.64,0:11:07.28,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,The empire that's persisted for \Ngenerations is God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.05,0:11:12.19,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,To defy God is preposterous!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.13,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.54,0:11:43.36,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,My, Your Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:45.93,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,You look absolutely heroic and elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.15,0:11:50.68,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Your late parents who died in an unfortunate \Naccident are certainly proud, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:52.14,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.51,0:11:57.94,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Shikoutazer can only be used by \Nthose of the royal bloodline.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:03.81,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,That said, you are, without doubt, \Nthe true emperor!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.37,0:12:05.37,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.41,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,I am the true heir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:09.75,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Your Excellency...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:11.37,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.07,0:12:24.05,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is what Stylish meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:26.73,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,The first and supreme Imperial Arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:35.34,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,This... This is the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.44,Default,Onset,0000,0000,0000,,How splendid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:41.95,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have this power, \Nno one can disobey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.95,0:12:43.40,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Everything will be ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.88,0:12:47.48,Default - italics,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,We'll turn a blind eye toward the \Ndestruction about to occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.57,Default - italics,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.57,0:12:52.26,Default - italics,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have the ignorant \Ncitizens rebuild it again
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.26,0:12:54.27,Default - italics,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,for the emperor and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.23,0:13:05.44,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,They're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.44,0:13:07.22,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of the emperor's guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.12,0:13:13.06,Default - italics,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.30,0:13:14.51,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.56,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing to your own kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.85,0:13:18.33,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Night Raid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.61,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,this is retribution for what you've begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:26.42,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,You're dragging civilians into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:27.90,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you call yourself an emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:29.07,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell do you think you're protecting?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.39,0:13:30.38,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.38,0:13:32.72,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,The empire's lasted for a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.72,0:13:35.41,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let it end with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.61,0:13:39.00,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, yes! That's exactly right, Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:42.46,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What does a thousand years \Nhave to do with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:47.39,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,I was born into the empire and \Ngiven this heavy responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:52.17,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,How could you know how I feel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.17,0:13:53.64,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I could never understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:58.19,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Because of you, many people are suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:07.91,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Look down and see what you're doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:21.93,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.93,0:14:23.73,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.73,0:14:25.45,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,If you let him sway you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:27.32,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,all we've done will be for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.32,0:14:29.97,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,You must harden your heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.16,0:14:32.60,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,H-He must be right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.35,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look away from me, you fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.37,0:14:47.30,Default,Soldiers,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.45,0:14:53.70,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you can do all this,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.91,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,fight the real evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:56.83,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:15:00.33,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with being a puppet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:03.29,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:08.88,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.54,0:15:11.09,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,I am the empire's soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.85,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,I fight to protect the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.85,0:15:15.47,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.98,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,A-And I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.06,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? When was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.65,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:29.18,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Emperor, please calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.18,0:15:30.82,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,This is now a holy war.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:33.45,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,There is no stopping this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:37.13,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop him, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.68,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only ones who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:42.17,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you don't have to tell me twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:43.36,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:46.30,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,You dare disobey the empire and emperor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:47.83,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.63,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't joined the rebel army.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:54.72,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Protecting the powerless is simply a soldier's duty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:15:59.67,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,What a troublesome guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.39,0:16:01.09,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.09,0:16:01.94,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:04.69,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,He is necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.91,0:16:14.06,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,Winged guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.06,0:16:15.20,Default,Leone,0000,0000,0000,,we'll settle this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:17.99,Default,Ran,0000,0000,0000,,No, we won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.52,0:16:22.29,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's too tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.75,Default - italics,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Even Grand Chariot can't break through.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.82,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,We can still fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:33.38,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,If we give up,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.22,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,it'll be over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.93,0:16:45.65,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.36,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.86,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:54.04,Default - flashback,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how sturdy something appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.04,0:16:56.28,Default - flashback,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,it should have some weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.38,0:17:00.79,Default - flashback,Susanoo,0000,0000,0000,,If you can discover that in battle, \Nit'll be very effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:02.33,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Su...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:03.53,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:04.79,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Create a gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.87,0:17:06.63,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.63,0:17:09.13,Default,Onest,0000,0000,0000,,Your Excellency, kill the traitors!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:12.80,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Those who betray the empire
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.09,0:17:14.55,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,receive the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.23,0:17:32.56,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,This one area's worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.56,0:17:35.16,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling such a large thing is a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.16,0:17:37.22,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's bound to be some damage somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:38.12,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Su?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.45,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.79,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.38,0:17:55.05,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.42,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going this far?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.97,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you... Give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.97,0:18:02.87,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.86,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Up till today, I've dealt with countless tragedies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.23,0:18:07.48,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I carry them all with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.40,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,all my fallen comrades!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:10.95,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.95,0:18:13.91,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,let them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.02,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have some painful, \Ndespair-ridden experiences.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:23.13,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, most of them will be tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:27.53,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,But we chose to walk this path.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.11,0:18:29.12,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.06,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take on the dirty work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:34.02,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,And change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:37.09,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,After we finish, we can disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.09,0:18:38.38,Default - italics,Tatusmi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.54,0:18:40.14,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,Shout it out, Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:42.35,Default - flashback,Bulat,0000,0000,0000,,With your raging spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.98,Default - italics,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Incursio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.36,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Made in ancient times,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.83,0:18:59.36,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,the evolving armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.29,0:19:12.96,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:16.84,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.61,0:19:27.58,Default,Emperpr,0000,0000,0000,,Fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.62,0:19:38.03,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi, you'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.71,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Like hell I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.99,0:19:41.53,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I made a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.54,0:19:52.04,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:53.50,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:10.14,Default,Wave,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.80,0:21:00.99,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:04.04,Default,Tatsumi,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like I couldn't keep my promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:16.79,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,You promised me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.24,0:21:19.31,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,You said you'd survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:21.48,Default,Akame,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.06,0:21:31.60,Default,Soldier,0000,0000,0000,,Is it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:37.32,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Did we lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.79,0:21:39.53,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Did the empire...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.53,0:21:40.44,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,Did I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.34,0:21:43.07,Default,Emperor,0000,0000,0000,,lose?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.32,0:21:52.26,Default,Esdeath,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsumi died.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.80,0:23:40.94,Title2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(322,1)} Akame ga Kill!
